0the%20way%20I%20raised%20my%20own%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a44ba703-1591-4eeb-9288-e0dd63554e9b%5C%22%3EIt%20felt%20like%20starting%20over%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20driving%20all%20over%20the%20city%20with%20them.%20It%20was%20the%20weirdest%20thing%20because%20I%20hadn't%20done%20that%20in%20so%20long.%20In%20PTA%20meetings%2C%20the%20teachers%20were%20looking%20at%20me%2C%20a%20gray-haired%20lady%2C%20probably%20thinking%20of%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20here%20with%20all%20these%20young%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20books%20at%20home%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrandparents-are-raising-teenage-grandkids-retirement-different-expectations-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrandparents%20raising%20grandchildren%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20was%20also%20an%20organization%20called%20Grandparents%20Raising%20Grandchildren%20at%20a%20local%20Jewish%20community%20center%20in%20New%20Orleans%20that%20I%20went%20to.%20For%20many%20of%20the%20other%20grandparents%20who%20were%20raising%20their%20grandchildren%2C%20their%20children%20were%20on%20drugs%20or%20had%20abandoned%20them.%20It%20was%20quite%20different%20from%20my%20situation%2C%20but%20it%20still%20helped%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20even%20know%20how%20I%20lived%20through%20it.%20I%20had%20plenty%20of%20problems.%20I%20love%20my%20grandchildren%2C%20and%20thank%20God%20they%20turned%20out%20all%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20of%20raising%20them%2C%20I%20realized%20you%20have%20to%20let%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20go%20and%20pick%20your%20battles.%20You%20can't%20always%20make%20it%20work%20the%20way%20you%20want%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20stop%20stressing%20myself%20out%20about%20it.%20I%20let%20them%20get%20away%20with%20a%20little%20more%20than%20I%20did%20with%20my%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251650434-0e1b-420d-bb08-75a47c825546%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20hard%20to%20get%20them%20to%2