tion-best-tips-chores-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eall%20the%20domestic%20responsibilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20I%20could%20focus%20full-time%20on%20my%20business%20and%20career.%20I've%20been%20growing%20my%20business%20ever%20since%2C%20to%20the%20point%20where%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20expand%20what%20I%20do%20to%20launch%20my%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flourishcourses.co.uk%2Fmidlife%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlourish%20Midlife%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20online%20program%20for%20women%20ages%2040%20to%2060.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-remotely-childcare-costs-career-growth-return-to-office-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewomen%20who%20work%20full-time%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20still%20also%20worrying%20about%20everything%20else%20%E2%80%94%20the%20running%20of%20the%20house%2C%20the%20ferrying%20around%20of%20the%20children%2C%20while%20often%20also%20looking%20after%20their%20older%20parents.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20it's%20worn%20like%20a%20badge%20of%20honor%20to%20be%20so%20busy%20and%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20have%20gone%20completely%20the%20other%20way.%20I%20don't%20cook.%20I%20don't%20clean.%20I%20don't%20do%20laundry.%20I%20don't%20get%20involved%20in%20anything%20domestic.%20And%20I'm%20completely%20shameless%20about%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d99058ba-8efb-4213-af59-8e6a62242521%5C%22%3EMy%20husband's%20job%20has%20more%20flexibility%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENeil%20still%20works%20full-time%20in%20insurance%2C%20but%20now%20fully%20from%20home%2C%20so%20he%20can%20fit%20in%20personal%20things%20around%20his%20working%20day.%20He%20has%20a%20senior%20role%20managing%20a%20team%2C%20so%20he%20can%20be%20flexible%2C%20whereas%20it's%20a%20bit%20more%20difficult%20for%20me%20when%20I%20have%20clients%20to%20see%20and%20am%20not%20available%20outside%20that.%20He%20also%20saves%20four%20hours%20a%20day%20by%20n