0my%20help%20with%20something%2C%20I%20would%2C%20of%20course%2C%20do%20it.%20The%20thing%20with%20boundaries%20is%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20rigid%20all%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20move%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20while%20I'm%20not%20feeling%20resentful%20anymore%2C%20and%20I'm%20in%20a%20joyous%20period%20of%20my%20life%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20Neil%20to%20become%20resentful%2C%20either.%20So%20we're%20always%20checking%20in%20with%20each%20other%20on%20how%20our%20work%20is%20doing%20and%20if%20we%20have%20enough%20gas%20in%20the%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeil%20is%20now%20more%20of%20a%20hands-on%20dad%20and%20husband%20than%20ever.%20And%20as%20for%20me%2C%20I'm%20flat%20out%20with%20a%20full%20caseload%20at%20work%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Neil%20is%20really%20supportive%20of%20that.%20He%20wants%20me%20to%20do%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-took-over-domestic-work-i-could-focus-on-career-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769610481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6978cb89d3c7faef0eccf9b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-took-over-domestic-work-i-could-focus-on-career-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sarah%20Turner%20explains%20how%20a%20midlife%20career%20shift%20led%20her%20husband%20to%20take%20on%20all%20domestic%20work%2C%20transforming%20their%20marriage%20and%20her%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(MaryLou%20Costa)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-took-over-domestic-work-i-could-focus-on-career-2026-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Play%20Rocky%E2%80%99%20opens%20Thanksgiving%202026%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769610431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3