20help%20me%20make%20more%20flattering%20choices%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222499%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lisa%20Cannon%20smiling%20in%20front%20of%20tree%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6977a601d3c7faef0eccec9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI've%20adjusted%20which%20shades%20I%20wear%20based%20on%20my%20color%20analysis.%20%3Cp%3ELisa%20Cannon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20I%20wasn't%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20some%20kind%20of%20miraculous%20makeover%20in%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20look%20unrecognizable%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20desperation%2C%20I%20turned%20to%20generative%20AI.%20I%20asked%20ChatGPT%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-figure-out-your-season-color-analysis-worth-it-2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecolor%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20I%20could%20understand%20which%20shades%20of%20makeup%20and%20clothing%20would%20look%20best%20on%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20uploaded%20a%20headshot%20taken%20in%20natural%20light%2C%20without%20makeup.%20Then%20I%20used%20a%20photo-editing%20tool%20to%20pinpoint%20the%20hexadecimal%20colors%20in%20my%20face%2C%20hair%2C%20eyes%2C%20and%20lips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20those%20colors%2C%20I%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20detect%20my%20undertones%20and%20contrast%20and%20tell%20me%20which%20%26quot%3Bseason%26quot%3B%20of%20shades%20would%20flatter%20me%20most.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20analysis%2C%20I'm%20a%20%26quot%3Bsoft%20autumn.%26quot%3B%20I%20learned%20that%20my%20most%20flattering%20colors%20were%20shades%20like%20olive%2C%20sage%2C%20camel%2C%20rose%2C%20and%20terracotta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20discovered%20that%20I%20should%20try%20to%20keep%20my%20wardrobe%20and%20accessories%20warm%20and%20subtle%20%E2%80%94%20never%20stark%20or%20icy.%20I'd%20been%20wearing%20black%20and%20white%20my%20whole%20