uld%20give%20my%20hair%20bounce%20and%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20fighting%20the%20natural%20wave%20of%20my%20hair%20all%20my%20life%2C%20but%20as%20I've%20gotten%20older%2C%20the%20waves%20have%20been%20winning.%20So%20I%20surrendered%20and%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257ff196a-dd5a-4bd7-b6ec-cedbd5e6a469%5C%22%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20looking%20better%20helps%20me%20feel%20better%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221438%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20%20Lisa%20Cannon%20smiling%20in%20front%20of%20paneling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6977a601e1ba468a96aab460%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20made%20changes%20that%20are%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20upkeep%20and%20sustain%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20%3Cp%3ELisa%20Cannon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20walked%20back%20into%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20in%20person%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20lot%20more%20confident.%20I%20felt%20I%20looked%20less%20like%20a%20crazy%20cat%20lady%20and%20more%20like%20a%20cool%20aunt.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20I%20told%20my%20team%20my%20real%20age%2C%20they%20all%20seemed%20gratifyingly%20shocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20I%20made%20some%20incremental%20improvements%20that%20didn't%20cost%20much%20and%20gave%20me%20a%20great%20return%20on%20my%20investment.%20What's%20even%20more%20important%20is%20that%20these%20efforts%20feel%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20spend%20a%20few%20minutes%20in%20the%20evening%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecrets-for-dressing-like-youre-rich-quiet-luxury-outfit-ideas-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echoosing%20an%20outfit%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20next%20day.%20I'm%20willing%20to%20devote%20more%20time%20in%20the%20morning%20doing%20makeup%20and%20hair.%20And%20it's%20certainly%20worth%20it%20to%20go%20to%20the%20salon%20for%20a%20cut