th%20finally%20descended%20the%20watch%20tower%2C%20relief%20colouring%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20in%20this%20story%20was%20a%20young%20Vivek%20Menon%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20dedicated%20to%20the%20preservation%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F236243%2Fganesh-chaturthi-wild-elephant-protection-love-heroes-conservation-protection-mahout-assam-tamil-nadu-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotection%20of%20wild%20habitats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20tryst%20with%20the%20elephant%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20made%20me%20understand%20the%20animal%E2%80%99s%20strength%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles%2C%20quick%20to%20add%2C%20however%2C%20that%20his%20love%20for%20the%20wild%20and%20nature%20predates%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20singular%20story%20that%20served%20as%20inspiration%20to%20become%20a%20conservationist%2C%20Menon%20insists.%20But%20coax%20him%20a%20little%2C%20and%20he%20says%20genetics%20did%20play%20its%20role%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20from%20Kerala%2C%20the%20land%20of%20elephants%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20as%20did%20childhood%20treks.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20were%20treks%20to%20the%20Himalayas%20during%20my%20school%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Menon%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20right%20to%20say%20that%20I%20took%20to%20animals%20and%20birds%20the%20moment%20I%20was%20exposed%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20room%20resembled%20an%20animal%20shelter.%20Birds%20and%20small%20animals%20rescued%20from%20the%20wild%20and%20predatory%20hands%20found%20a%20safe%20space.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20I%20was%20doing%20them%20%5Bthe%20animals%5D%20good%20by%20bringing%20them%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20justifies.%20Today%2C%20at%2056%2C%20the%20conservationist%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20that%20same%20goodwill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHow%20many%20hours%20I%20have%20spent%20watching%20young%20bulls%20playfully%20test%20their%20strength%2C%20their%20nascent%20ivories%20never%20inflicting%20harm%2C%20their%20trunks%20loosely%20entwined%20%26amp%3B%20ears%20aflap%20while%20muscle%20and%20sinew%20grind%20against%20the%20other.%20These%20young%20mock-battles%20train%20them%20for%20later%20adult%20life!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEm9soIlOnY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FEm9soIlOnY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Vivek%20Menon%20(%40vivek4wild)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvivek4wild%2Fstatus%2F1802908763894186253%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F171244%2Fkarnataka-farmer-forest-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20for%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20when%20he%20digressed%20from%20the%20career%20plans%20his%20father%20had%20for%20him%20%E2%80%94%20a%20career%20in%20automobile%20engineering%20%E2%80%94%20and%20followed%20his%20heart%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20zoology%20laboratory%2C%20no%20one%20was%20shocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20concerning%20animals%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestion%3A%20Is%20there%20a%20better%20way%20to%20interview%20a%20conservationist%20than%20reaching%20him%20through%20a%20Zoom%20call%20while%20he%20is%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20South%20African%20jungle%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbsolutely%20not%3B%20just%20what%20is%20needed%20to%20add%20essence%20to%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMenon%E2%80%99s%20excitement%20was%20palpable.%20As%20senior%20advisor%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98International%20Fund%20for%20Animal%20Welfare%E2%80%99%20for%20years%20now%2C%20he%20was%20in%20the%20Southern%20African%20country%20assisting%20in%20an%20operation%20that%20involved%20radio%20collaring%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F260553%2Fwildlife-conservation-elephants-save-school-teacher-hero-west-bengal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelephants%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20process%20in%20which%20a%20collar%20with%20an%20attached%20radio%20transmitter%20is%20put%20on%20an%20animal%20so%20that%20its%20movements%20in%20its%20natural%20habitat%20can%20be%20remotely%20monitored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20he%20jokingly%20adds%2C%20my%20interview%20call%20is%20interrupting%20something%20very%20important%20that%20he%E2%80%99d%20otherwise%20be%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20watching%20150%20elephants%20against%20the%20setting%20sun%20in%20Zimbabwe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%20has%20watched%20Menon%20around%20elephants%20would%20testify%20that%20the%20two%20share%20a%20bond.%20He%20understands%20them.%20And%20the%20relationship%20is%20reciprocal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubstantial%20proof%20of%20his%20love%20for%20the%20wild%20lies%20in%20the%20five%20organisations%20that%20he%20has%20created%20%E2%80%94%20TRAFFIC%20India%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wildlife%20trade%20monitoring%20network%3B%20NGO%20Srishti%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20founded%20to%20protect%20the%20environment%20in%20Delhi%3B%20Delhi%20Bird%20Club%3B%20Venu%20Menon%20Animal%20Allies%20Foundation%3B%20and%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20(WTI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wild%20elephant%20herd%20in%20Keonjhar%2C%20Odisha%5C%22%20src